.Dd $Mdocdate: May 9 2020 $
.Dt rwmtx_wrlock 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm rwmtx_wrlock
.Nd acquire a write lock
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Lb threads
.In threadse.h
.Ft int
.Fn rwmtx_wrlock "rwmtx_t *rw"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The function
.Fn rwmtx_wrlock
will acquire a write lock on the given read/write lock
.Fa rw .
If a read lock is acquired on the lock, the thread will be stalled until
the write lock can be acquired.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
Upon success
.Fn rwmtx_wrlock
will return 
.Va thrd_success .
In case of error
.Va thrd_error
will be returned.
.Sh SEE ALSO
